QuestData.Title: Upheaval
QuestData.Description:
We're surrounded by the dead, dying, and other detritus.
Feels like war, does it not?
Oculeth and others have gone ahead to see to the soldiers.
Perhaps you ought to see to them as well?
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Chief Telemancer Oculeth at the top of the waterfall.
